<title>INDIA: India's Infosys up 4 pct ahead of bonus.</title>
<headline>India's Infosys up 4 pct ahead of bonus.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-04-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares of software firm Infosys Technologies jumped 52.25 rupees, or 4.2 percent, to 1,295 in early trade on the Bombay bourse on Monday as investors bought ahead of a bonus share issue, traders said.  </p>
<p>The firm's board of directors is due to meet on Tuesday to announce a bonus issue of shares and finalise financial results for 1996/97 (April-March).</p>
<p>Dealers said the market expected the firm to announce an issue of one bonus share for every one share held.</p>
<p>Infosys shares had gained 10 percent on Friday after the firm announced it planned to issue bonus shares.</p>
